def calc_avg_std(nums):
    
    avg = sum(nums)/len(nums)  # Calculate Average
    variance = sum((x - avg)**2 for x in nums) / len(nums)  # Calculate Variance
    std = variance**0.5  # Calculate Standard Deviation
    
    return avg, std  # Return the average and standard deviation

if __name__ == '__main__':
    print(calc_avg_std([1,2,3,4]))
